flowchart TD
    Caller([Caller / Client])
    Facade[__init__.py<br/>Public API Facade]
    Orchestrator[core.Orchestrator<br/>submit / resume]
    WFRegistry[(workflows.py<br/>WORKFLOW_REGISTRY<br/>templates)]
    Checkpoint[(checkpoint.py<br/>CheckpointStore<br/>JSON files)]
    Runner[runner.run_step<br/>retry loop]
    AgentRegistry[(agents.py<br/>AGENT_REGISTRY)]
    Agent[Agent.execute<br/>dispatcher]
    MockExec[Mock Executor]
    ClaudeExec[claude_code_executor]
    ClaudeCLI[[claude CLI<br/>subprocess]]
    ToolRegistry[(tools.py<br/>TOOL_REGISTRY)]
    PermGate{Permission<br/>allowed?}
    ToolImpl[Tool Implementation]
    Models[(models.py<br/>Workflow / Step<br/>shared context dict)]

    Caller -->|submit request_type, payload| Facade
    Facade --> Orchestrator
    Orchestrator -->|get_workflow_template| WFRegistry
    WFRegistry -->|template steps| Orchestrator
    Orchestrator -->|build Workflow| Models
    Orchestrator -->|save / load JSON| Checkpoint
    Checkpoint -->|hydrated Workflow| Orchestrator

    Orchestrator -->|sequential for each step| StepLoop{More steps?}
    StepLoop -->|yes| Runner
    StepLoop -->|no| Done([Workflow COMPLETED])

    Runner -->|lookup agent| AgentRegistry
    AgentRegistry --> Agent
    Runner -->|resolve inputs_from| Models

    Agent -->|mock mode| MockExec
    Agent -->|real mode| ClaudeExec
    ClaudeExec -->|subprocess.run --print| ClaudeCLI
    ClaudeCLI -->|stdout / timeout 300s| ClaudeExec
    MockExec -->|outputs dict| Runner
    ClaudeExec -->|outputs dict| Runner

    Runner -->|invoke_tool name, kwargs| ToolRegistry
    ToolRegistry --> PermGate
    PermGate -->|denied| ToolErr[PermissionError]
    PermGate -->|allowed| ToolImpl
    ToolImpl -->|result| Runner

    Runner -->|write step.output<br/>mutate Step in place| Models
    Models -->|workflow.context&#91;step.name&#93;| StepLoop

    Runner -->|on failure| Retry{retries left?}
    Retry -->|yes| Runner
    Retry -->|no| Failed([Step FAILED])

    Runner -->|after each step| Checkpoint
    Failed -->|resume rewinds<br/>to first non-terminal| Orchestrator
